(108, 'Mommi', 'uploads/resturant/1485016541955.png,uploads/resturant/1485016541573.png,uploads/resturant/1485016541345.png,uploads/resturant/1485016541988.png,uploads/resturant/1485016541152.png,uploads/resturant/1485016541330.png', '22', '', '51.4640934', '-0.1323714', '44-48 Clapham High St, London SW4 7UR', 0, 'Trendy Japanese-Peruvian restaurant with great food and a lively crowd.\r\n\r\nSouth London''s favourite late-night drinking and dining spot where Japan meets Latin America in an urban, cool environment. Great choice for a fun and lively evening out or weekend brunch.\r\n\r\nOne last word: 100% Gluten free!\r\n\r\nOpening times:\r\n\r\nMonday to Wednesday: 5.30pm - 11pm\r\n\r\nThursday: 5.30pm - Midnight\r\n\r\nFriday: 5.30pm - 1am\r\n\r\nSaturday: 11am - 2am\r\n\r\nSunday: 11am - 11pm', 7, '8,16', '6,7,8,10', '7', '5', '11:00', '21:00', 7, '17:30', '21:00', 1, '17:30', '22:00', 2, '17:30', '22:00', 3, '17:30', '22:00', 4, '17:30', '23:00', 5, '17:30', '23:00', 6, 121, 1, '2017-03-20 14:59:05', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(110, 'Massis Grill & bar', 'uploads/resturant/1485883629301.png,uploads/resturant/1485883629715.png,uploads/resturant/1485883629666.png,uploads/resturant/1485883629247.png,uploads/resturant/1485883629822.png,uploads/resturant/1485883629570.png', '29', '', '51.5188732', '-0.1796229', 'Paddington Central, 9 Sheldon Square, London W2 6HY', 0, 'Gorgeous Lebanese restaurant with a large outdoor seating area, perfect for summer alfresco dining in beautiful waterfront sorroundings.\r\n\r\nMassis is a great spot for business lunches as well as date nights. The restaurant overlooks the newly developed Paddington Central waterfront. Sit in an enjoy some belly-dancing entertainment or dine al fresco style on a beautiful summer evening and watch the sun slowly melt into the River Thames. Either way, you are on to a winner with this one.\r\n\r\nOne last word: One of the best alfresco spots in central London!\r\n\r\nOpening times\r\n\r\nMonday â€“ Thursday: 12noon â€“ 11pm\r\n\r\nFriday â€“ Saturday: 12noon â€“ 11:30pm\r\n\r\nSunday: 12noon â€“ 10:30pm', 8, '20', '3,6,8,10', '5,6,8', '5', '12:00', '22:00', 7, '12:00', '22:30', 1, '12:00', '22:30', 2, '12:00', '22:30', 3, '12:00', '22:30', 4, '12:00', '22:30', 5, '12:00', '22:30', 6, 123, 1, '2017-03-07 12:08:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
