(144, 'Yosma', 'uploads/resturant/1486226038592.png,uploads/resturant/1486226038437.png,uploads/resturant/1486226038746.png,uploads/resturant/1486226038722.png,uploads/resturant/1486226038745.png,uploads/resturant/1486226038316.png', '14', '', '51.5186652', '-0.1557891', '50 Baker St, Marylebone, London W1U 7BT', 0, 'A trendy and exciting Turkish restaurant in the heart of Marylebone.\r\n\r\nDesigned by award winning studio, Afroditi Krassa, its contemporary interior is inspired by Istanbul''s vast history and culture. Executive Chef Hus Vedat (ex Barbecoa and Caxton Grill) heads up the kitchen here, serving up his signature pit-roasted grills and much more.\r\n\r\nOne of our exciting new finds, Yosma is a great place to enjoy sharing platters with friends in Marylebone. \r\n\r\nOne last word: Perfect grills, great ambience!\r\n\r\nOpening Times:\r\n\r\nMonday to Wednesday: 12noon - 11pm\r\nThursday to Friday: 12noon - midnight\r\nSaturday to 10am - midnight\r\nSunday to 10am - 11pm', 8, '36', '6,7,8,10', '5,8', '5', '12:00', '22:00', 7, '12:00', '22:00', 1, '12:00', '22:00', 2, '12:00', '22:00', 3, '12:00', '22:00', 4, '12:00', '22:30', 5, '10:00', '22:30', 6, 157, 1, '2017-03-27 15:45:09', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(145, 'Romulo Cafe', 'uploads/resturant/1485007566605.png,uploads/resturant/1485007566989.png,uploads/resturant/1485007566536.png,uploads/resturant/1485007566211.png,uploads/resturant/1485007566600.png,uploads/resturant/1485007566359.png', '5', '', '51.4975007', '-0.2029526', '343 Kensington High St, Kensington, London W8 6NW', 0, 'London''s favourite Filipino restaurant and bar in the heart of Kensington.\r\n\r\nOne of our favourite new restaurants in Kensington, Romulo CafÃ© London is the perfect spot to savor the very best of Philippine-inspired cuisine in London. The venue comprises four separate dining areas each with its own unique feature and inspiration. \r\n\r\nOne last word: Donâ€™t forget to ask about the Chef-inspired homemade ice cream...we approve!\r\n\r\nOpening times:\r\n\r\nMonday to Saturday: \r\nLunch: 12noon - 3pm\r\nDinner: 5pm to 12midnight\r\n\r\nSunday: 12noon - 11:30pm', 8, '6', '6,7,8,10', '5,7,8', '4', '12:00', '23:00', 7, '12:00', '23:00', 1, '12:00', '23:00', 2, '12:00', '23:00', 3, '12:00', '23:00', 4, '12:00', '23:00', 5, '12:00', '23:00', 6, 158, 1, '2017-03-06 18:29:31', '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
