(212, 'OPSO', 'uploads/resturant/1487109000100.png,uploads/resturant/1487777687937.png,uploads/resturant/1487777687423.png,uploads/resturant/1487777687878.png,uploads/resturant/1487777687673.png,uploads/resturant/1487777687214.png', '14', '', '51.5208229', '-0.1528894', '10 Paddington St, Marylebone, London W1U 5QL', 0, 'Greek restaurant in Marylebone extremely popular with Greeks in London as well as international diners.\r\n\r\nOPSO is an ancient Greek word for a delectable morsel of food, a delicacy and this trendy prime central London restaurant and bar fully reflects this concept. Inspired by traditional and contemporary Greek tastes, OPSO prides itself on creating modern Greek tapas using high quality ingredients sourced directly from Greece. A commendable social venue, its food concept is based on modern Greek tapas style to be shared and enjoyed between family and friends.\r\n\r\nOne last word: Inspired by Greece...made in London\r\n\r\nOpening times:\r\n\r\nMonday - Friday\r\nDinner: 6pm - 11:30pm \r\n\r\nSaturday\r\nBrunch: 10am - 5pm\r\nDinner: 5pm - 11:30pm \r\n\r\nSunday\r\nBrunch: 10am - 5pm\r\nDinner: 5pm - 11pm ', 8, '31,35', '3,6,8,10,11', '5,6,7,8,9', '5', '10:00', '21:30', 7, '18:00', '22:00', 1, '18:00', '22:00', 2, '18:00', '22:00', 3, '18:00', '22:00', 4, '18:00', '22:00', 5, '10:00', '22:00', 6, 225, 1, '2017-03-17 17:17:27', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
