(220, 'Kiri', 'uploads/resturant/1487851960599.png,uploads/resturant/1487851960414.png,uploads/resturant/1487851960816.png,uploads/resturant/1487851960388.png,uploads/resturant/1487851960213.png,uploads/resturant/1487851960549.png', '1', '', '51.513801', '-0.147187', '22-23 Woodstock St, Mayfair, London WC1 2AR', 0, 'Warm and cosy Japanese restaurant near Oxford street feautring modern Izakaya dishes.\r\n\r\nTucked away down a side road close to Oxford Street is Kiri, a Japanese restaurant specialising in modern izakaya dishes and an exclusive sake list. The decor has a homely and calming feel, with natural woods and warm lighting throughout as well as several cosy corners for an intimate meal out. Thereâ€™s also some outside seating for the warmer months.\r\n\r\nOne last word: Amazing food, fantastic service and a down to earth atmosphere...these guys know how to keep it simple!\r\n\r\nOpening times:\r\n\r\nMonday to Friday\r\nLunch: 12noon - 3pm\r\nDinner: 6pm - 11pm\r\n\r\nSaturday\r\nLunch: 12:30pm - 3:30pm\r\nDinner: 6pm -11pm\r\n\r\nSunday: Closed', 8, '8', '8,10', '5,12', '5', '', '', 0, '12:00', '22:00', 1, '12:00', '22:00', 2, '12:00', '22:00', 3, '12:00', '22:00', 4, '12:00', '22:00', 5, '12:30', '22:00', 6, 233, 1, '2017-03-07 09:26:58', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(221, 'Picture Marylebone', 'uploads/resturant/1487608871448.png,uploads/resturant/1487608871110.png,uploads/resturant/1487608871181.png,uploads/resturant/1487608871277.png,uploads/resturant/1487608871183.png,uploads/resturant/1487608871175.png', '14', '', '51.5189052', '-0.1504487', '19 New Cavendish St, Marylebone, London W1G 9TZ', 0, 'A trendy, independent restaurant serving groundbreaking British cuisine. \r\n\r\nPicture Marylebone embraces all that is great about Marylebone - classy and elegant yet warm and relaxed. Enjoy small ingredient-led dishes and value-driven set menus in an elegant, light-filled dining room. This venue is a great spot for dining out with friends or that special someone.\r\n\r\nOne last word: Delectable food in an elegant atmosphere...we recommend the six-course menu reasonably priced at Â£45pp\r\n\r\nOpening times:\r\n\r\nMonday â€“ Saturday\r\nLunch: 12noon â€“ 2:30pm \r\nDinner: 6pm â€“ 10:30pm\r\n\r\nSundays Closed', 8, '25', '6,8,10,11', '5', '5', '', '', 0, '12:00', '21:00', 1, '12:00', '21:00', 2, '12:00', '21:00', 3, '12:00', '21:00', 4, '12:00', '21:00', 5, '12:00', '21:00', 6, 234, 1, '2017-03-07 11:50:29', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(222, 'Picture Fitzrovia', 'uploads/resturant/1487609385243.png,uploads/resturant/1487609385415.png,uploads/resturant/1487609385893.png,uploads/resturant/1487609385113.png,uploads/resturant/1487609385318.png,uploads/resturant/1487609385202.png', '4', '', '51.5194027', '-0.142201', '110 Great Portland St, Fitzrovia, London W1W 6PQ', 0, 'Extremely popular neighbourhood British restaurant in Fitzrovia.\r\n\r\nPicture is from a trio who met in London and shared a common dream of opening their own restaurant. Tom, Alan and Colin worked together for many years within Michelin-starred restaurants before deciding it was time to begin their own venture. \r\n\r\nPicture Fitzrovia opened in June 2013 and quickly established itself as part of the local community. Close relationships have been formed with many locals who return frequently. The team also enjoy welcoming those guests travelling to us from further away for a special lunch or dinner experience.\r\n\r\nOne last word: Delectable food in an elegant atmosphere...we recommend the six-course menu reasonably priced at Â£45pp\r\n\r\nOpening times:\r\n\r\nMonday â€“ Saturday\r\nLunch: 12noon â€“ 2:30pm \r\nDinner: 6pm â€“ 10:30pm', 8, '25', '6,8,10', '5', '5', '', '', 0, '12:00', '21:00', 1, '12:00', '21:00', 2, '12:00', '21:00', 3, '12:00', '21:00', 4, '12:00', '21:00', 5, '12:00', '21:00', 6, 235, 1, '2017-03-07 12:12:20', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
