(230, 'Quilon', 'uploads/resturant/1487715306748.png,uploads/resturant/1487715306373.png,uploads/resturant/1487715306735.png,uploads/resturant/1487715306637.png,uploads/resturant/1487715306734.png', '10', '', '51.4986732', '-0.1376867', '41 Buckingham Gate, Westminster, London SW1E 6AF', 0, 'A stunning one Michelin star restaurant serving costal cuisine from the Taj Group of hotels. \r\n\r\nQuilon is an elegant restaurant which boasts one of London''s most popular meet-up bars. The menu features a ''Coastal Cuisine'' and serves dishes such as seafood, crustacea, char-grilled shrimps with lime and chilli, lobster with tangy Goan pickle and fish curry with coconut. Quilon was awarded its first Michelin star in 2008 and received a Wine Spectator Award of Excellence in 2009.\r\n\r\nOne last word: After dinner, drop into the extremely popular Q Bar for the signature â€˜Qojitoâ€™ cocktail or a glass of champagne...\r\n\r\nOpening Times\r\n\r\nMonday to Friday\r\nLunch: 12noon - 2:30pm\r\nDinner: 6pm - 11pm\r\n\r\nSaturday \r\nLunch: 12.30pm - 3.30pm\r\nDinner: 6pm - 11pm\r\n\r\nSunday \r\nLunch: 12.30pm - 3.30pm\r\nDinner: 6pm - 10.30pm \r\n\r\n', 8, '9,39', '3,4,5,6,7', '5,8', '5', '18:00', '21:00', 7, '18:00', '22:00', 1, '12:00', '21:30', 2, '12:00', '21:30', 3, '12:00', '22:00', 4, '21:00', '22:00', 5, '21:00', '22:00', 6, 243, 1, '2017-03-17 10:21:03', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
