(234, 'Rocket Bishopsgate', 'uploads/resturant/1489879795578.png,uploads/resturant/1489879795346.png,uploads/resturant/1489879795842.png,uploads/resturant/1489879795954.png,uploads/resturant/1489879795898.png,uploads/resturant/1489879795742.png', '9', '', '51.5208237', '-0.0791353', 'Broadgate, 201 Bishopsgate, London EC2M 3AB', 0, 'One of Bishopsgate''s landmark bar restaurants, Rocket is well-loved by trendy city professionals and perfect for business lunches and after work drinks. \r\n\r\nLocated less than 3 minutes walk from Liverpool Street, the venue features a large and spacious bar and restaurant on the ground floor and a mezzanine level private bar perfect for more intimate moments.\r\n \r\nDishes here are packed full of fresh, bold & unique flavours. Inspired by the â€˜BIGâ€™ combination salads originating in California, combined with just the best Neapolitan style gourmet pizza and  the fusion of amazing flavours of Asia. \r\n\r\nOne last word: One of the city of London''s trendiest bar restaurants, so expect a fun and frenetic atmosphere!\r\n\r\nOpening times:\r\n\r\nMonday-Friday:\r\nFrom 10am till late\r\n\r\nSaturdays:\r\nFrom 11am till late \r\n\r\nClosed on Sundays', 8, '34,35', '3,7,10', '5,7,8', '5', '', '', 0, '10:00', '22:00', 1, '10:00', '22:30', 2, '10:00', '22:30', 3, '10:00', '23:00', 4, '10:00', '23:00', 5, '11:00', '23:00', 6, 247, 1, '2017-03-18 23:29:55', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(235, 'Rocket, The City', 'uploads/resturant/1488667136747.png,uploads/resturant/1488667136252.png,uploads/resturant/1488667136154.png,uploads/resturant/1488667136988.png,uploads/resturant/1488667136871.png,uploads/resturant/1488667136591.png', '9', '', '51.5144917', '-0.0844384', '6, Adam''s Court, Old Broad St, London EC2N 1DX', 0, 'Highly popular restaurant and bar in the City of London featuring excellent Mediterranean dishes and an extensive drinks menu.\r\n\r\nLocated on Adams Court - a pedestrian courtyard just off Old Broad Street and Threadneedle Street; and within a 2-minute walk from Bank station, Rocket has been serving up great experiences to trendy city folks for sometime now. \r\n\r\nThe venue comprises three floors each with its own unique ambience and there is definitely something for everyone in this trendy city-style restaurant bar. Head to the second floor if you''d like some initmacy!\r\n\r\nOne last word: Looking for a great venue to impress your clients without breaking the bank? This is it!\r\n\r\nOpening times:\r\n\r\nMonday - Friday: 9am till late\r\n\r\nClosed on Saturday & Sunday', 8, '34,35', '3,7,10', '5,7,8', '5', '', '', 0, '12:00', '22:00', 1, '12:00', '22:00', 2, '12:00', '22:30', 3, '12:00', '22:30', 4, '12:00', '22:30', 5, '', '', 0, 248, 1, '2017-03-17 10:25:58', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
