(237, 'Vasco & Piero''s Pavilion', 'uploads/resturant/1490629286818.png,uploads/resturant/1490629286111.png,uploads/resturant/1490629286422.png,uploads/resturant/1490629286624.png,uploads/resturant/1490629286333.png,uploads/resturant/1490629286450.png', '7', '', '51.5147516', '-0.1370038', '15 Poland Street, Soho, London W1F 8QE', 0, 'Extremely popular Italian restaurant with a daily changing menu in Soho.\r\n\r\nBrimming with history and class, â€˜Vasco and Piero opened the restaurant in 1971 above the much revered, and now sadly lost, Academy cinema in Oxford Street. The Pavilion, a former Hungarian tea room, was owned by the cinemaâ€™s founder, and director of the acclaimed â€˜Murder in the Cathedralâ€™, George Hoellering. \r\n\r\nFeaturing a twice-daily changing menu, you are guaranteed a uniquely different experience each time you dine here. Particular favourites are truffles, wild mushrooms, seasoned cheeses and cured meats such as lombetto and capocollo. A magnet for public figures due to its rich history, this venue is perfect for an evening out with close friends or that special someone.\r\n\r\nOne last word: To relive moments of London''s golden cinema age, ask to see the history gallery in the private room located in the basement!\r\n\r\nOpening Times:\r\n\r\nMonday to Friday\r\nLunch: 12.15 - 2.30pm\r\nDinner: 5.30pm - 10pm\r\n\r\nSaturday\r\nDinner: 5.30pm - 10pm\r\n\r\nClosed on Sunday ', 8, '28', '3,5,6,8,11', '5', '5', '', '', 0, '12:30', '21:30', 1, '12:30', '21:30', 2, '12:30', '21:30', 3, '12:30', '21:30', 4, '12:30', '21:30', 5, '17:30', '21:30', 6, 250, 1, '2017-03-27 15:41:27', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(238, 'Caviar House & Prunier', 'uploads/resturant/1488748246421.jpeg,uploads/resturant/1488748246660.jpg,uploads/resturant/1488748246751.jpg,uploads/resturant/1488748246101.jpg,uploads/resturant/1488748246999.jpg,uploads/resturant/1488748246823.jpg', '11', '', '51.5076205', '-0.1406407', '161 Piccadilly, St. James''s, London W1J 9EA', 0, 'The birth of exceptional caviarâ€¦ In the midst of several hectares of land on the banks of the Dordogne near Bordeaux, the Prunier factory produces its caviar with its unique expertise in a fully controlled environment.\r\n\r\nOur experts select the best sturgeon, Acipenser Baeri, originating from Siberia which can reach up to 3 metres long and can weigh several hundred kilos. This sturgeon grows particularly well in captivity and produces its caviar after 8 years. From the spawning period to when they grow into small fish, our experts take constant care of our sturgeon kept in natural water from the Isle river, a tributary of the Dordogne.As soon as the caviar master estimates the ideal fishing date, he uses salting technique developed over 86 years ago, to obtain exceptional caviar.\r\n\r\nCaviar House & Prunier guarantees a constant quality of caviar by managing every step of the production process, from fishing the sturgeon to tasting the caviar.\r\n\r\nAvailable for delivery within the United Kingdom, European Union and Switzerland. The Prunier Caviar range includes:\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', 8, '41', '5', '11', '', '12:00', '18:00', 7, '10:00', '21:00', 1, '10:00', '21:00', 2, '10:00', '21:00', 3, '10:00', '21:00', 4, '10:00', '21:00', 5, '10:00', '21:00', 6, 251, 1, '2017-03-31 20:36:59', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(239, 'Daylesford', 'uploads/resturant/1488749041435.jpg,uploads/resturant/1488749041800.jpg,uploads/resturant/1488749041339.jpg,uploads/resturant/1488749041997.jpg,uploads/resturant/1488749041866.jpg,uploads/resturant/1488749041923.jpg', '12', '', '51.5145337', '-0.2007065', '208-212 Westbourne Grove, London W11 2RH', 0, 'At Daylesford, we have created a special brand of hampers available for delivery anywhere within the United Kingdom\r\n\r\nIf orders are placed before 12noon Monday â€“ Friday we endeavour to dispatch your order on a next day delivery. In the circumstance that we are unable to fulfil your order due to stock availability we will call and email you to advise on the next best delivery day, or suggest a substitute.\r\n\r\n If you would prefer to receive your delivery on a date different to that of next day, please specify in the â€˜order notesâ€™ as you check out.', 8, '41', '5', '5', '', '12:00', '18:00', 7, '10:00', '22:00', 1, '10:00', '22:00', 2, '10:00', '22:00', 3, '10:00', '22:00', 4, '10:00', '22:00', 5, '10:00', '22:00', 6, 252, 1, '2017-03-09 21:58:55', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(240, 'Les Deux Salons', 'uploads/resturant/1488812217852.jpg,uploads/resturant/1488812217872.jpg,uploads/resturant/1488812217809.jpg,uploads/resturant/1488812217729.jpg,uploads/resturant/1488812217518.jpg,uploads/resturant/1488812217419.jpg', '8', '', '51.5096586', '-0.1262772', '40 - 42 William IV St, London WC2N 4DD', 0, 'Elegant French restaurant from Prescott & Conran located near Trafalgar square.\r\n\r\nFrom a tray of oysters to entrecÃ´te frites and, of course, great French cheese, Les Deux Salons menu is full of French favourites. Guests can enjoy everything from a plate of charcuterie before curtain up to a three-course meal. Itâ€™s a relatively large menu, offering a range of dishes from light and fine to gutsy and generous. The all-French wine list includes over 20 wines available by the glass and 375ml carafe.\r\n\r\nOne last word: A casual afternoon bite or an impressive first date, this elegant venue does the trick!\r\n\r\nOpening times:\r\n\r\nMonday - Saturday: 11:30am â€“ 12.30 after midnight\r\n\r\nLate supper until 10.45pm on Monday & Tuesday and until 11.15pm from Wednesday to Saturday', 6, '26', '5,6,7,11', '5', '5', '', '', 0, '12:00', '22:30', 1, '12:00', '22:30', 2, '12:00', '22:30', 3, '12:00', '22:30', 4, '12:00', '22:30', 5, '12:00', '22:30', 6, 253, 1, '2017-03-07 09:35:33', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(242, 'HUNter 486', 'uploads/resturant/1489879376630.jpg,uploads/resturant/1489879376256.jpg,uploads/resturant/1489879376234.jpg,uploads/resturant/1489879376953.JPG,uploads/resturant/1489879376607.JPG,uploads/resturant/1489879376521.jpg', '14', '', '51.5159214', '-0.1598794', '50 Great Cumberland Pl, Marylebone, London W1H 7FD', 0, 'Elegant yet relaxed hotel restaurant and bar serving meaty grills and stone-baked pizzas.\r\n\r\nThe Arch Hotelâ€™s creative HUNter 486 Restaurant and Bar, named after the 1950s dialling code for Marylebone, presents a â€˜Best of Britishâ€™ inspired menu carefully developed by Head Chef, Gary Durrant. They offer British classics like Fish & Chips and Afternoon Tea has a twist, influenced by Londonâ€™s diverse and multicultural street food scene.\r\n\r\nThe vibrant Bar area features original designer chairs by Tom Dixon, dazzling glass chandeliers, and a wonderful array of delicious liquid refreshments including the hotelâ€™s signature Grace Kelly Martini. This place is perfect for business lunches and dinners as well as Sunday roasts with the family and loved ones.\r\n\r\nOne last word:  The Sunday roast is a must...priced reasonably at Â£22.95 for two-courses. It is truly the stuff of legends!', 8, '25', '3,5,6,7', '5', '5', '12:00', '22:00', 7, '12:00', '22:30', 1, '12:00', '22:30', 2, '12:00', '22:30', 3, '12:00', '22:30', 4, '12:00', '22:30', 5, '12:00', '22:30', 6, 255, 1, '2017-03-18 23:22:57', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(245, 'Boyds Grill & Wine Bar', 'uploads/resturant/1489094320864.jpg', '10', '', '51.506935', '-0.126012', '8 Northumberland Ave, Westminster, London WC2N 5BY', 0, 'Showcasing British artisanal ingredients combined with international cooking techniques and fine wines by the glass in a historic Victorian interior. Boyds Grill & Wine Bar is located in the heart of central London, by Trafalgar Square, The Strand, Charing Cross and Whitehall.\r\n\r\nBREAKFAST\r\n7am â€“ 11am (Sat 7.30am â€“ 12pm) (Sun 8am â€“ 12pm)\r\n\r\nLUNCH\r\n12pm â€“ 3pm (Mon â€“ Fri)\r\n\r\nDINNER\r\n5pm â€“ 10pm (Mon â€“ Sat)\r\n\r\nKITCHEN BAR\r\n12pm â€“ 10pm (Mon â€“ Sat)', 8, '25', '3,5,6,7', '5', '5', '08:00', '22:00', 7, '07:30', '22:00', 1, '07:00', '22:00', 2, '07:00', '22:00', 3, '07:00', '22:00', 4, '07:00', '22:00', 5, '07:00', '22:00', 6, 258, 1, '2017-03-31 20:45:12', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(259, 'Mint Leaf Haymarket', 'uploads/resturant/1489872766204.png,uploads/resturant/1489872766745.png,uploads/resturant/1489872766289.png,uploads/resturant/1489872766697.png,uploads/resturant/1489872766953.png,uploads/resturant/1489872766251.png', '1', '', '51.5082013', '-0.1310752', 'Suffolk Pl, London SW1Y 4HX', 0, 'Serving Modern Indian cuisine in elegant surroundings, Mint Leaf offers a unique dining experience in the heart of the West End and Theatreland just minutes from Trafalgar Square and Piccadilly Circus.\r\n\r\nMint Leaf''s versatile menu features authentic ingredients prepared in a contemporary style and served in the intimate restaurant whilst an exciting array of cocktails can be enjoyed in the luxurious bar.\r\n\r\nA popular haunt with entertainers and the theatre world, recent visitors to Mint Leaf include Justin Bieber, Pixie Lott, Daniel Radcliffe, Daniel Lukakis, Zara Holland, Abigail Clarke, Christopher Biggins, Chloe Goodman, Lizzie Cundy to name just a few. . .\r\n\r\nOne last word: Arguably the most sophisticated Indian restaurant in London!\r\n\r\nOpening times:\r\n\r\nMonday - Wednesday\r\nLunch: 12noon - 3pm\r\nDinner: 5pm - 11pm\r\n\r\nThursday & Friday\r\nLunch: 12noon - 3pm\r\nDinner: 5pm - 11.30pm\r\n\r\nSaturday\r\nDinner: 5pm - 11.30pm\r\n\r\nSunday\r\nDinner: 5pm - 11pm\r\n\r\nThe bar is open until midnight from Sunday to Wednesday and until 1am from Thursday to Saturday.', 8, '9,10', '3,5,6,7,11', '5,6,8', '5', '17:00', '23:00', 7, '12:00', '23:00', 1, '12:00', '23:00', 2, '12:00', '23:00', 3, '12:00', '23:00', 4, '12:00', '23:00', 5, '07:00', '23:00', 6, 272, 1, '2017-03-21 11:22:29', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(260, 'Mint Leaf Lounge', 'uploads/resturant/1489874849852.png,uploads/resturant/1489874849250.png,uploads/resturant/1489874849602.png,uploads/resturant/1489874849956.png,uploads/resturant/1489874849529.png,uploads/resturant/1489874849102.png', '9', '', '51.5150448', '-0.0877904', '12 Angel Ct, London EC2R 7HB', 0, 'Popular high-end restaurant near the Bank of England in the heart of the City.\r\n\r\nAn elegant venue where guests can enjoy sophisticated dining with menus combining authentic, seasonal Indian ingredients with contemporary cooking techniques and stylish presentation. \r\n\r\nThe striking cocktail bar and mezzanine level are backed by captivating light features, long translucent drapes, snake-skin booths and comfy sofas which make this a sumptuous retreat for the discerning guest.\r\n\r\nOne last word: Extremely popular business venue in the City...the cocktails are a must!\r\n\r\nOpening Times\r\n\r\nMonday to Friday\r\nLunch: 11:30am - 3pm\r\nDinner: 5:30pm - 11pm\r\n\r\nThe bar is open until 12 midnight on Monday and Tuesday and until 1am from Wednesday to Friday', 8, '9,10', '3,5,6,7', '5,6,8', '5', '', '', 0, '17:00', '23:00', 1, '17:00', '23:00', 2, '17:00', '23:00', 3, '17:00', '23:00', 4, '13:30', '23:00', 5, '', '', 0, 273, 1, '2017-03-18 22:20:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(261, 'L''Anima', 'uploads/resturant/1489877398657.png,uploads/resturant/1489877398396.png,uploads/resturant/1490717378177.jpg,uploads/resturant/1490717378868.jpg,uploads/resturant/1490717378668.jpg,uploads/resturant/1490717378444.jpg', '9', '', '51.5216432', '-0.0819205', '1 Snowden St, London EC2A 2DQ', 0, 'High-end Italian restaurant near Liverpool Street popular with the business crowd.\r\n\r\nTranslated as â€˜soulâ€™ in Italian, award-winning Lâ€™Anima is true to its name, specialising in authentic, honest Italian cuisine made with all the passion of chefs with Italian cooking in their blood. \r\n\r\nThe Southern-influenced cuisine reinterprets dishes from Sardinia, Puglia and Sicily. An extensive list of award-winning wines sourced from environmentally friendly producers from the less well-known regions of Calabria, Lombardy and Emilia Romagna.\r\n\r\nOne last word: Some of the best and most extensive collection of fine wines in the city of London...\r\n\r\nOpening Times:\r\n\r\nMonday to Friday\r\nLunch: 11.45am - 3pm\r\nDinner: 5.30pm - 11pm\r\n\r\nClosed on Saturday and Sunday', 8, '28', '3,5,11', '5', '6', '', '', 0, '17:30', '22:30', 1, '17:30', '22:30', 2, '17:30', '22:30', 3, '17:30', '22:30', 4, '17:30', '22:30', 5, '', '', 0, 274, 1, '2017-03-28 16:09:39', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(262, 'Shezan', 'uploads/resturant/1489878320433.png,uploads/resturant/1489878320833.png,uploads/resturant/1489878320552.png,uploads/resturant/1489878320661.png,uploads/resturant/1489878320450.png,uploads/resturant/1489878320323.png', '2', '', '51.4988806', '-0.1667944', '16-22 Cheval Pl, Knightsbridge, London SW7 1ES', 0, 'Candlelit Pakistani restaurant near Harrods with an ornate backdrop of Mughal paintings and artefacts.\r\n\r\nNo visit to London is complete without experiencing London''s vast curry scene and they do not come much better than Shezan. Enjoying a 40-year-long legacy, this venue has attracted a string of celebrities and royalty over the years for its exquisite Indian and Pakistani cuisine and magical ambience.\r\n\r\nGuest can choose to dine at the table or on floor mats for the more adventurous diners. A popular spot for visitors from the Middle East and international visitors, you can expect to see anyone here.\r\n\r\nOne last word: Traditional Pakistani and Indian cuisine in a uniquely elegant ambience!\r\n\r\nOpening Times:\r\n\r\nMonday to Sunday: 12noon - 11pm\r\n', 8, '43', '3,5,10', '5,6,8', '5', '12:30', '22:00', 7, '12:30', '22:30', 1, '12:30', '22:30', 2, '12:30', '22:30', 3, '12:30', '22:30', 4, '12:30', '22:30', 5, '12:30', '22:30', 6, 275, 1, '2017-03-21 16:03:42', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(263, 'Meat House London', 'uploads/resturant/1489932619675.jpg,uploads/resturant/1489932619619.jpg,uploads/resturant/1489932619890.png,uploads/resturant/1489932619377.png,uploads/resturant/1489932619370.png,uploads/resturant/1489932619140.jpg', '31', '', '51.5310711', '-0.1181646', 'Pentonville Rd, Kings Cross, London N1 9JP', 0, 'Newly opened steakhouse in Kings Cross serving up generous portions of meat.\r\n\r\nWith leather-style brown seating throughout, no expenses seem to have been spared in decking this place out. Serving only Halal certified meat, Meat House London is growing its reputation as one of the best steakhouses in the city.\r\n\r\nA perfect spot for a casual dinner in Kings Cross, the venue also operates a late bar serving a wide selection of great cocktails.\r\n\r\nOne last word: Head here for some carnivorous indulgence...the portions are generous!\r\n\r\nOpening times:\r\n\r\nMonday to Sunday: 12noon  - 12 midnight', 8, '38', '10', '5,6', '4', '12:00', '22:00', 7, '12:00', '22:00', 1, '12:00', '22:00', 2, '12:00', '22:00', 3, '12:00', '22:00', 4, '12:00', '22:00', 5, '12:00', '22:00', 6, 276, 1, '2017-03-19 14:19:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(264, 'Amesta with Arzak Instruction', 'uploads/resturant/1490186945405.jpg,uploads/resturant/1490186945386.jpg,uploads/resturant/1490186945125.jpg,uploads/resturant/1490186945843.jpg,uploads/resturant/1490186945775.jpg,uploads/resturant/1490186945797.jpg', '3', '', '51.5007826', '-0.1520507', 'COMO The Halkin, London, The Halkin by Como, Halkin Hotel London, Halkin St, Belgravia, London SW1X 7DJ', 0, 'Elegant one Michelin Star restaurant in Belgravia showcasing the very best of Basque cuisine.\r\n\r\nAmetsaâ€™s approach is rooted in the traditions of â€˜New Basque Cuisineâ€™, pairing the earthy flavours and techniques of Spainâ€™s Basque region with modern, surprising twists featuring locally-sourced and organic produce from land and sea. \r\n\r\nThe restaurantâ€™s interior was designed by London-based Ab Rogers Design, who took inspiration from the raw aesthetic of the original Arzak restaurant in San Sebastian, Spain, which holds three Michelin-stars.\r\n\r\nOne last word: An ideal venue for business meetings and date nights in Belgravia!\r\n\r\nOpening Times:\r\n\r\nLunch\r\nTuesday - Friday: 12pm - 2pm\r\nSaturday: 12:30pm - 2pm\r\n\r\nDinner\r\nMonday - Saturday: 6:30pm - 10pm', 8, '29', '3,4,5,6,7,8', '5', '5', '', '', 0, '18:30', '22:00', 1, '18:30', '22:00', 2, '18:30', '22:00', 3, '18:30', '22:00', 4, '18:30', '22:00', 5, '18:30', '22:00', 6, 277, 1, '2017-03-29 14:50:58', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
