(98, 'Taxi & Limousines', 'uploads/service_image/1484548175ic6.png', 1, '<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000"><strong>Terms &amp; Conditions and Privacy Policy (</strong></span></span><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">Last Updated on&nbsp;17 February 2017)</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000"><strong>Part A: Terms &amp; Conditions</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">These Terms &amp; Conditions (the &#39;Terms&#39;) (together with the documents referred to in it) tell you the terms on which you may make use of our complimentary concierge app (the &lsquo;App&rsquo;) to discover and book local experiences including restaurants, deliveries, taxis, health clubs, leisure attractions and other services which we may add from time to time.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">Please read these Terms carefully before you start to use the App, as these will apply to your use of the App. By using the App, you confirm that you have read and accepted these Terms and that you agree to comply with them. If you do not agree to these Terms, you must not use the App. The App is owned and operated by podd Technologies, a part of Infiniti Finance Technologies Limited, a company registered in England and Wales under number 09374836 with its registered office at 1 Theatre Street, London SW11 5NE (podd Technologies&#39;, &#39;we&#39;, &#39;our&#39;, and &#39;us&#39;).</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">1. Introduction</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-