span style="color:#000000">By clicking on &lsquo;Book&rsquo;, &lsquo;Book Now&rsquo;, &lsquo;Order&rsquo; and &lsquo;Order Now&rsquo; you acknowledge that you have made a Booking Request which is subject to confirmation by the service provider.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">In order to make a booking request through the App, you must enter your name and phone number. You acknowledge that these details will be passed on to third party service providers listed on the App who may contact you using these details.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">You may also provide your email address although this is optional and not required. You acknowledge that your email address will be passed on to third party service providers who may contact you using these details. These emails may also include marketing and promotional materials not related to your booking.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">By providing the details above, you consent to being contacted by third party service providers in this way.</span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">6. Booking Confirmation</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">&nbsp; 6.1 You acknowledge that all booking requests are subject to acceptance by the service provider at their sole discretion.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">&nbsp; 6.2 Where your booking is accepted, you will receive a Booking Confirmation by text on the mobile number provided and/ or by email within a reasonable time.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">&nbsp; 6.3 Where your booking is declined or otherwise not accepted, the only recourse available to you is to look for an alternative service provider within the App or outside the App by your own efforts.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">&nbsp; 6.4 You acknowledge that by making a booking you will be under an obligation to pay the service provider for any products and services rendered including food and drink provided by the restaurant, and, where applicable, service fees charged by the restaurant as well as taxi fares, experience bookings, health club bookings; agreed with the taxi operator.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">&nbsp; 6.5 You acknowledge that service providers may cancel or amend bookings after they have been confirmed. We are not responsible for any cancelled or amended bookings. Please contact the service provider directly if you have any queries.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">&nbsp; 6.6 If you wish to amend a booking, you will need to discuss this with the service provider directly. We cannot guarantee that the service provider will be able to accommodate any changes.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">7. Making Payments with the App</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">&nbsp; 7.1 In some instances, you may be required to make a payment for a booking through the App.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">&nbsp; 7.2 In order to pay a bill using the App, you will need to enter your debit or credit card information. You acknowledge that payment processing services are provided by a third party.â€¨</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">&nbsp; 7.3 You warrant that you have appropriate authority to use the payment card details which you input. By inputting your debit or credit card information, you agree to use of that information by secure third party payment providers for the purpose of paying your bill and processing your payment.â€¨</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">&nbsp; 7.4 Your card details will be stored securely by third party payment providers. We do not store your payment card details on our systems.â€¨</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">8. Intellectual Property Rights and Use of the App</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">&nbsp; 8.1 We grant you a non-exclusive, non-transferable licence to use a copy of the App for the purposes of the services offered by the App only, which include (where applicable in relation to each service) to make reservations and bookings and receive tailored offers from, service providers listed on the App.â€¨</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">&nbsp; 8.2 We are the owner or the licensee of all intellectual property rights in the App, and in the material published on it. Tho