of our rights and obligations under these Terms to that third party or the newly merged entity.â€¨</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 11pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">1.7 All legal notices in relation to the App or these Terms should be given in writing and addressed to </span><a href="mailto:hello@poddapp.com"><span style="color:#000000">hello@poddapp.com</span></a></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">2. The App</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">&nbsp; &nbsp;2.1 We may update the App from time to time, and may change the content at any time. However, &nbsp;please note that any of the content on the App may be out of date at any given time, and we are under no obligation to update it.â€¨</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">&nbsp;&nbsp; 2.2&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">We do not guarantee that the App, or any content on it, will be free from errors or omissions.â€¨</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">3. Accessing the App</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">&nbsp; &nbsp;3.1 The App made available free of charge.â€¨</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">&nbsp; 3.2 We provide the App on an &quot;as is&#39; and &quot;as available&quot; basis with all faults. We do not guarantee that the App, or any content on it, will always be available or be uninterrupted. Access to the App is permitted on a temporary basis. We may suspend, withdraw, discontinue or change all or any part of the App without notice. You agree that your use of the App is at your own risk. We will not be liable to you if for any reason any of the App are unavailable at any time or for any period.â€¨</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">&nbsp; 3.3 You are responsible for making all arrangements necessary for you to have access to the App. You are also responsible for ensuring that all persons who access the App through your serviced apartment or hotel are aware of these Terms and other applicable terms and conditions, and that they comply with them.â€¨</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">&nbsp; 3.4 To the maximum extent permitted by law, we disclaim any and all implied conditions and warranties that the App and the services available through them are of satisfactory quality, accurate, fit for a particular purpose, or non-infringing.â€¨</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">4. Eligibility</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 11pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">4.1 You must be 18 years or older to use the App and the content and services provide through them. By using the App, you represent and warrant that you are 18 years or older.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">5. Making a Booking Request through the App</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">By clicking on &lsquo;Book&rsquo;, &lsquo;Book Now&rsquo;, &lsquo;Order&rsquo; and &lsquo;Order Now&rsquo; you acknowledge that you have made a Booking Request which is subject to confirmation by the service provider.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">In order to make a booking request through the App, you must enter your name and phone number. You acknowledge that these details will be passed on to third party service providers listed on the App who may contact you using these details.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">You may also provide your email address although this is optional and not required. You acknowledge that your email address will be passed on to third party service providers who may contact you using these details. These emails may also include marketing and promotional materials not related to your booking.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">By providing the details above, you consent to being contacted by third party service providers in this way.</span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">6. Booking Confirmation</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">&nbsp; 6.1 You acknowledge that all booking requests are subject to acceptance by the service provider at their sole discretion.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">&nbsp; 6.2 Where your booking is accepted, you will receive a Booking Confirmation by text on the mobile number provided and/ or by email within a reasonable time.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">&nbsp; 6.3 Where your booking is declined or otherwise not accepted, the only recourse available to you is to look for an alternative service provider within the App or outside the App by your own efforts.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">&nbsp; 6.4 You acknowledge that by making a booking you will be under an obligation to pay the service provider for any products and services rendered including food and drink provided by the restaurant, and, where applicable, service fees charged by the restaurant as well as taxi fares, experience bookings, health club bookings; agreed with the taxi operator.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">&nbsp; 6.5 You acknowledge that service providers may cancel or amend bookings after they have been confirmed. We are not responsible for any cancelled or amended bookings. Please contact the service provider directly if you have any queries.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">&nbsp; 6.6 If you wish to amend a booking, you will need to discuss this with the service provider directly. We cannot guarantee that the service provider will be able to accommodate any changes.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">7. Making Payments with the App</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">&nbsp; 7.1 In some instances, you may be required to make a payment for a booking th