are protected by copyright, trade marks, database right and other intellectual property rights. All such rights are reserved.â€¨</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">&nbsp; 8.3&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">You may not without our prior written consent (except to the extent required in order to use the App in accordance with these Terms) copy, sell, reproduce, publish, modify, or distribute any of the content published, displayer or performed on the App or systematically extract such content or in any way use or exploit commercial any such content.â€¨</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">9. Limitation of Our Liability</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">&nbsp; 9.1 Nothing in these Terms excludes or limits our liability for death or personal injury arising from our negligence, or our fraud or fraudulent misrepresentation, or any other liability that cannot be excluded or limited by English law.â€¨</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">&nbsp; 9.2 To the extent permitted by law, we exclude all conditions, warranties, representations or other terms which may apply to the App or any content on it, whether express or implied.â€¨</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">&nbsp; 9.3 We will not be liable to any user for any loss or damage, whether in contract, tort (including negligence), breach of statutory duty, or otherwise, even if foreseeable, arising under or in connection with: use of, or inability to use, the App; or use of or reliance on any content displayed on the App.â€¨</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">&nbsp; 9.4 Please note that we only provide the App for domestic and private use. You agree not to use the App for any commercial or business purposes, and we have no liability to you for any loss of profit, loss of business, business interruption, or loss of business opportunity.â€¨</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">10. Viruses</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">&nbsp; 10.1 We do not guarantee that the App will be secure or free from bugs or viruses.â€¨</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">&nbsp; 10.2 You must not misuse the App by knowingly introducing viruses, trojans, worms, logic bombs or other material which is malicious or technologically harmful. You must not attempt to gain unauthorised access to the App, the server on which the App is stored or any server, computer or database connected to the App.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">11. Applicable Law</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 11pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">11.1 These Terms, its subject matter and its formation (and any non-contractual disputes or claims) are governed by English law. We both agree to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts of England and Wales.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left: 11pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">â€¨</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000"><strong>Part B: Privacy Policy</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">Podd Technologies, a part of Infiniti Finance Technologies (&quot;podd&quot;, &quot;us&quot;, &quot;we&quot;, or &quot;our&quot;) operates the services available through the podd mobile application (the &quot;Service&quot;). This page informs you of our policies regarding the collection, use, processing and disclosure of data that identifies or is associated with you (your&quot; Personal Information&quot;) when you use our Service.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">For the purposes of the Data Protection Act 1998(the&quot; Act&quot;), podd is the data controller of Personal Information we hold about you. We will not use or share your information with anyone except as described in this Privacy Policy. We use your Personal Information for providing and improving the Service. By using the Service, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy. We work with partners who facilitate bookings at some of our restaurants, bars, taxis, health clubs and attractions (&quot;Booking Partners&quot;) and third parties that provide payment services to you through the interface provided by our Service (&quot;Payment Providers&quot;).</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">By agreeing to podd&rsquo;s terms and conditions you are also agreeing to allow (&quot;Booking Partners&quot;) to use your personal data as set out in the Booking Partners User Agreement (available upon request).</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000"><strong>Information Collection and Use</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">While using our Service, we may ask you to provide us with certain Personal Information that can be used to contact or identify you. Personal Information may include, but is not limited to, your email address, name, phone number, and other information. The list below sets out in more detail the categories of Personal Information we collect about you and how we use that information.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">Contact details: We collect contact information such as your name, your email address, your telephone number and addresses associated with you, your account or any reservation or booking you make with us. We will use your contact details so that we can communicate with you directly about the Services we provide, to facilitate providing our Service to you and about queries, issues or concerns you or other users of our website or app have. We will transfer your contact information to the applicable Booking and service partners to facilitate making your reservation. When you choose to make a payment using a Payment Provider through our Service, we will also disclose your contact information, such as your name, telephone number, and email address, to the Payment Provider and/or the service partner&rsquo;s payment services provider to verify your identity, so that your payment can be processed and your payment card charged the transaction amount.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">Payment and transaction information: We may ask for you to provide us your payment card details and transfer such information to the applicable Booking Partner and/or service provider to facilitate making your reservation. We do not collect or store any payment card details and do not at any time receive your payment.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">Information about your location: As part of our Service we make suggestions and provide content based on location data you provide to us. Other than information you choose to provide to us, we do not collect information about your precise location. To ensure that our suggestions and content are as relevant as possible, The Internet Protocol (&quot;IP&quot;) address of the computer, tablet, smartphone or other electronic device you connect to our website or app, may help us determine your approximate location. We may store the location data you provide to us and we will use this data to help improve and customize our Service, and provide analytics regarding the use of our Service using location data, for example understanding how many users make a booking based on our location based suggestions or in which location(s) our Service is used most often. For the avoidance of doubt but this will be no more precise than the city, state or country you are using your device in. We may use an approximate location to ensure content on the site is relevant to the city, state or country you are in. We will not collect or track data regarding your exact location unless you are using our service without your consent. If you give us permission to use and store information about your precise location, we use this information to provide features of our Service, to improve and customize our Service.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">Information about fraudulent or criminal activity relating to your account: We will use information about fraudulent or criminal activity relating to your use of our App for the purposes of detecting and preventing fraud or crime.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">We may anonymise and aggregate any of the information we collect (so that it does not directly identify you). We may use anonymised information for purposes that include testing our IT systems, research, data analysis, improving the website and developing new products and features.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000"><strong>Service Providers</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">In addition to Booking Partners and Payment Providers we may employ third party companies and individuals to facilitate our Service, to provide the Service on our behalf, to perform Service-related services or to assist us in analysing how our Service is used. These third parties have access to your Personal Information only to perform these tasks on our behalf and are obligated not to disclose or use it for any other purpose not explicitly set out in this Privacy Policy.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000"><strong>Communications</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">We may use your Personal Information to contact you with newsletters, marketing or promotional materials and other information that may be of interest to you, including marketing and promotional content and offers through SMS, email, app push notifications and/or newsletters. You may opt out of receiving any, or all, of these communications from us by following the unsubscribe link or instructions provided in any email or SMS we send or through your phone settings.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">Similarly, the Personal Information we provide to the Booking Partner and / or service partner to facilitate a reservation may be used by the Booking Partner, Service Partner or their selected business partners to contact you with newsletters, marketing, promotional materials and other information which may be of interest to you through SMS, email or app push notifications. You may opt out of receiving these communications following the instructions provided in the relevant SMS or email or through your phone settings.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000"><strong>Compliance with Laws</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">We will disclose your Personal Information where required to do so by law or subpoena or if we believe that such action is necessary to comply with the law and the reasonable requests of law enforcement or to protect the security or integrity of our Service.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000"><strong>Business Transaction</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">Your Personal Information may be disclosed or transferred to buyers of, investors in or lenders to, or (on terms of confidentiality) prospective buyers of, investors in or lenders to our business or any of our assets as part of a sale of our business or any of our assets.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000"><strong>Security</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">The security of your Personal Information is important to us, but remember that no method of transmission over the Internet, or method of electronic storage is 100% secure. While we strive to use commercially acceptable means to protect your Personal Information, we cannot guarantee its absolute security.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000"><strong>International Transfer</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">Your Personal Information is stored in electronic and physical records maintained by us and/or our service providers. Whilst we are based in the United Kingdom, our service providers may have servers located overseas, where the laws may not give the same level of protection to personal data as within the United Kingdom. By submitting your Personal Information, you agree that we may transfer, store or process your Personal Information in this way.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">We will take all steps reasonably necessary to ensure that your data is treated securely and in accordance with this Privacy Policy.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000"><strong>Children&#39;s Privacy</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">Our Service does not address anyone under the age of 12 (a &quot;Child&quot;). We do not knowingly collect Personal Information from children under 12. If you are a parent or guardian and you are aware that your Child has provided us with Personal Information, please contact us using the email shown on this page. If we discover that a child under 12 has provided us with Personal Information, we will delete such information from our servers immediately.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000"><strong>Access to your Personal Information</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">If you would like to access a copy of the Personal Information which we hold about you, then please send a request by email or by post using the appropriate contact details below. Your request to access a copy of the Personal Information which we hold about you may be subject to a fee of &pound;10 to meet our costs in providing you with this information. You have the right, in certain circumstances, to object to us processing your Personal Information or to request that your Personal Information is corrected or deleted. If you would like to exercise your right, then please contact us using the details below.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes. When we make a significant change to this Privacy Policy, we will update the &quot;last modified&quot; date at the top of this page and may require you to accept the new terms in accordance with our Terms and Conditions.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000"><strong>Contact Us</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000">Questions, comments and requests regarding these Terms should be sent by email to hello@poddapp.com</span></span></p>', '2017-01-16 06:29:53');
