(1, 'Restaurant && Bars', '<p><strong>Terms &amp; Conditions and Privacy Policy (</strong>Last Updated on&nbsp;17 February 2017)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Part A: Terms &amp; Conditions</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>These Terms &amp; Conditions (the &#39;Terms&#39;) (together with the documents referred to in it) tell you the terms on which you may make use of our complimentary concierge app (the &lsquo;App&rsquo;) to discover and book local experiences including restaurants, deliveries, taxis, health clubs, leisure attractions and other services which we may add from time to time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please read these Terms carefully before you start to use the App, as these will apply to your use of the App. By using the App, you confirm that you have read and accepted these Terms and that you agree to comply with them. If you do not agree to these Terms, you must not use the App. The App is owned and operated by podd Technologies, a part of Infiniti Finance Technologies Limited, a company registered in England and Wales under number 09374836 with its registered office at 1 Theatre Street, London SW11 5NE (podd Technologies&#39;, &#39;we&#39;, &#39;our&#39;, and &#39;us&#39;).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1. Introduction</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1.1 These Terms constitute the agreement between you and us for the use of the App and the contents and services available through them.â€¨</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1.2 This policy sets out the terms on which we process any personal data we collect from you, or that you provide to us. By using the App, you consent to such processing and you warrant that all data provided by you is accurate.â€¨</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1.3 We may change these Terms from time to time. Any changes we may make to these Terms in the future will be posted on this page. Please review this page frequently to see any updates or changes to these Terms.â€¨</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1.4 If we do not exercise or enforce any legal right or remedy which may be available to us, this will not be taken to be a formal waiver of our rights.â€¨</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1.5 If any part of these Terms shall be unlawful or unenforceable for any reason, this shall not affect the remainder of these Terms and that part shall be limited or eliminated to the minimum extent necessary so that these Terms shall otherwise remain in full force and effect.â€¨</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1.6 If we are acquired by, or merge with, a third party, we may transfer any or all of our rights and obligations under these Terms to that third party or the newly merged entity.â€¨</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1.7 All legal notices in relation to the App or these Terms should be given in writing and addressed to hello@poddapp.com.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. The App</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;2.1 We may update the App from time to time, and may change the content at any time. However, &nbsp;please note that any of the content on the App may be out of date at any given time, and we are under no obligation to update it.â€¨</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; 2.2&nbsp;We do not guarantee that the App, or any content on it, will be free from errors or omissions.â€¨</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3. Accessing the App</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;3.1 The App made available free of charge.â€¨</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; 3.2 We provide the App on an &quot;as is&#39; and &quot;as available&quot; basis with all faults. We do not guarantee that the App, or any content on it, will always be available or be uninterrupted. Access to the App is permitted on a temporary basis. We may suspend, withdraw, discontinue or change all or any part of the App without notice. You agree that your use of the App is at your own risk. We will not be liable to you if for any reason any of the App are unavailable at any time or for any period.â€¨</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; 3.3 You are responsible for making all arrangements necessary for you to have access to the App. You are also responsible for ensuring that all persons who access the App through your serviced apartment or hotel are aware of these Terms and other applicable terms and conditions,