e to us and we will use this data to help improve and customize our Service, and provide analytics regarding the use of our Service using location data, for example understanding how many users make a booking based on our location based suggestions or in which location(s) our Service is used most often. For the avoidance of doubt but this will be no more precise than the city, state or country you are using your device in. We may use an approximate location to ensure content on the site is relevant to the city, state or country you are in. We will not collect or track data regarding your exact location unless you are using our service without your consent. If you give us permission to use and store information about your precise location, we use this information to provide features of our Service, to improve and customize our Service.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Information about fraudulent or criminal activity relating to your account: We will use information about fraudulent or criminal activity relating to your use of our App for the purposes of detecting and preventing fraud or crime.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We may anonymise and aggregate any of the information we collect (so that it does not directly identify you). We may use anonymised information for purposes that include testing our IT systems, research, data analysis, improving the website and developing new products and features.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Service Providers</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition to Booking Partners and Payment Providers we may employ third party companies and individuals to facilitate our Service, to provide the Service on our behalf, to perform Service-related services or to assist us in analysing how our Service is used. These third parties have access to your Personal Information only to perform these tasks on our behalf and are obligated not to disclose or use it for any other purpose not explicitly set out in this Privacy Policy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Communications</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We may use your Personal Information to contact you with newsletters, marketing or promotional materials and other information that may be of interest to you, including marketing and promotional content and offers through SMS, email, app push notifications and/or newsletters. You may opt out of receiving any, or all, of these communications from us by following the unsubscribe link or instructions provided in any email or SMS we send or through your phone settings.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Similarly, the Personal Information we provide to the Booking Partner and / or service partner to facilitate a reservation may be used by the Booking Partner, Service Partner or their selected business partners to contact you with newsletters, marketing, promotional materials and other information which may be of interest to you through SMS, email or app push notifications. You may opt out of receiving these communications following the instructions provided in the relevant SMS or email or through your phone settings.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Compliance with Laws</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We will disclose your Personal Information where required to do so by law or subpoena or if we believe that such action is necessary to comply with the law and the reasonable requests of law enforcement or to protect the security or integrity of our Service.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Business Transaction</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Your Personal Information may be disclosed or transferred to buyers of, investors in or lenders to, or (on terms of confidentiality) prospective buyers of, investors in or lenders to our business or any of our assets as part of a sale of our business or any of our assets.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Security</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The security of your Personal Information is important to us, but remember that no method of transmission over the Internet, or method of electronic storage is 100% secure. While we strive to use commercially acceptable means to protect your Personal Information, we cannot guarantee its absolute security.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>International Transfer</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Your Personal Information is stored in electronic and physical records maintained by us and/or our service providers. Whilst we are based in the United Kingdom, our service providers may have servers located overseas, where the laws may not give the same level of protection to personal data as within the United Kingdom. By submitting your Personal Information, you agree that we may transfer, store or process your Personal Information in this way.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We will take all steps reasonably necessary to ensure that your data is treated securely and in accordance with this Privacy Policy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Children&#39;s Privacy</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Service does not address anyone under the age of 12 (a &quot;Child&quot;). We do not knowingly collect Personal Information from children under 12. If you are a parent or guardian and you are aware that your Child has provided us with Personal Information, please contact us using the email shown on this page. If we discover that a child under 12 has provided us with Personal Information, we will delete such information from our servers immediately.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Access to your Personal Information</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you would like to access a copy of the Personal Information which we hold about you, then please send a request by email or by post using the appropriate contact details below. Your request to access a copy of the Personal Information which we hold about you may be subject to a fee of &pound;10 to meet our costs in providing you with this information. You have the right, in certain circumstances, to object to us processing your Personal Information or to request that your Personal Information is corrected or deleted. If you would like to exercise your right, then please contact us using the details below.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes. When we make a significant change to this Privacy Policy, we will update the &quot;last modified&quot; date at the top of this page and may require you to accept the new terms in accordance with our Terms and Conditions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Contact Us</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Questions, comments and requests regarding these Terms should be sent by email to hello@poddapp.com</p>');
